{"tid":766578,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"攝取過多的脂肪會被排出體外？脂肪並不是致肥元兇？","createTime":"2018-08-03T16:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T10:45:10.000Z","uid":142825,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d1662b0072e9564b587ab5dc72524a424574de3","tid":766578,"uid":142825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:44:10.000Z","msg":"最近在看到一篇文章，說其實脂肪不是導致人長胖的元兇，因為身體會把攝取多余的脂肪排出體外，就像蛋白質一樣。但我好像記得中學上生物課的時候學過，脂肪會在體內最後分解成糖。<br />\n<br />\n所以我的疑惑是，吃進去的脂肪到底是會全部分解為糖？還是一部分？還是當身體供糖不足是才會分解？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人可以幫我解解這個疑惑嗎？（正處於減肥）"},{"pid":"5675a98d7c1a249a2d9db93695d33e691aaddf22","tid":766578,"uid":91664,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:59:15.000Z","msg":"讀緊中幾？"},{"pid":"fc0da54d486992178a717d4b70a75fdaa63ac7bd","tid":766578,"uid":63075,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:01:34.000Z","msg":"一餐食過多 脂肪的確未必有足夠膽汁<br />\n同消化得晒"},{"pid":"289d48fd4fa8c2443b77d309e3305dc64eb5e883","tid":766578,"uid":142825,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5675a98d7c1a249a2d9db93695d33e691aaddf22","tid":766578,"uid":91664,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:59:15.000Z","msg":"讀緊中幾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:07:58.000Z","msg":"讀緊高級文憑，本身唔係理科生，所以想請教下。<br />\n喺Facebook 度見到篇嘢。<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/207147/%E7%87%9F%E9%A4%8A%E5%B8%AB%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E7%98%A6-%E6%B2%B9%E8%86%A9%E5%98%A2%E6%9C%80%E6%98%93%E8%82%A5-%E7%B3%96%E8%83%BD%E5%9B%A4%E7%A9%8D%E8%AE%8A%E8%82%A5%E8%86%8F%E5%85%88%E4%BF%82-%E5%85%83%E5%87%B6?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F207147%2F%25E7%2587%259F%25E9%25A4%258A%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E7%2598%25A6-%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E8%2586%25A9%25E5%2598%25A2%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2598%2593%25E8%2582%25A5-%25E7%25B3%2596%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%259B%25A4%25E7%25A9%258D%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%2582%25A5%25E8%2586%258F%25E5%2585%2588%25E4%25BF%2582-%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2587%25B6%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=Y33Wh5SlbbBhD2ieEQzgBIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=cec99942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/207147/%E7%87%9F%E9%A4%8A%E5%B8%AB%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E7%98%A6-%E6%B2%B9%E8%86%A9%E5%98%A2%E6%9C%80%E6%98%93%E8%82%A5-%E7%B3%96%E8%83%BD%E5%9B%A4%E7%A9%8D%E8%AE%8A%E8%82%A5%E8%86%8F%E5%85%88%E4%BF%82-%E5%85%83%E5%87%B6?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a>"},{"pid":"edefdb2007e489ca15e38670b10defb108082670","tid":766578,"uid":19958,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"唔洗理你食緊既原素，要明既只有呢樣道理<br />\n假設你一日消耗卡路里係2000，無論你食乜都好，超過2000就會肥，少過2000就會瘦，就係咁簡單<br />\nCarbs fat protein 既比例因應唔同既訓練吸收量都會唔同"},{"pid":"36d530328e5ef3ed56d7d6d46afabd8f0e45591b","tid":766578,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LW9WmnNrfQ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLW9WmnNrfQ8&d=Y33Wh5SlbbBhD2ieEQzgBIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=3922a8ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LW9WmnNrfQ8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20160911/55625779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160911%2F55625779&d=Y33Wh5SlbbBhD2ieEQzgBIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=3913dad0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160911%2F55625779&h=37a1c5df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20160911/55625779</a>"},{"pid":"8eea1e7ad50b736fdb3098fad6938ced39e2e43d","tid":766578,"uid":9115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:39:57.000Z","msg":"利申,鳩吹<br />\n<br />\n其實肥胖係因為運動不足<br />\n一個人如果唔需要任何運動就可以生存到<br />\n咁到底肥定瘦對生存有幫助呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n答案係肥。<br />\n因為肥胖代表佢儲存左大量能量<br />\n假設突發性糧食不足,肥人一定生存得耐過瘦人。<br />\n身體就係基於呢個原則,為左提升生存率,而儲存大量能量。<br />\n<br />\n講返轉頭,點解運動有助減肥呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先,身體係唔識判斷點解你要運動嘅<br />\n身體會認為你所進行嘅一切運動<br />\n都係短期生存所必須<br />\n例如,跑係為左逃避危險等等。<br />\n<br />\n於是身體因應你所需嘅運動量調節<br />\n例如肌肉量,增加肌肉量可以大力d,不過常駐消耗都會變大<br />\n身體於是為左減少消耗,就會調節肌肉量至下限。<br />\n<br />\n咁,脂肪又點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實同肌肉一樣會自我調節。<br />\n脂肪雖然係有效儲存能量嘅方式<br />\n但係過多就會阻礙身體運動。<br />\n咁當身體發現肥胖會阻礙運動<br />\n就會判斷短期生存優先於長遠生存<br />\n咁就會調節,減少體內儲存量,提升運動能力<br />\n咁就可以真正減到肥啦。<br />\n<br />\n再講多次,利申,鳩吹"},{"pid":"2f2ffb5b7b62fdf02ec3a2ce308e1b4df79ba321","tid":766578,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:48:23.000Z","msg":"首先 你要知道脂肪係咩黎<br />\n之後你就要理解脂肪細胞點解會擴大<br />\n最後你就會知脂肪會唔會自然排出體外"},{"pid":"69a5e2a0de86af576e8868b29f8ffb559a458c33","tid":766578,"uid":142825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc0da54d486992178a717d4b70a75fdaa63ac7bd","tid":766578,"uid":63075,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T17:01:34.000Z","msg":"一餐食過多 脂肪的確未必有足夠膽汁<br />\n同消化得晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06613d46723d9504529ddd6c97fa625203c8fa00","tid":766578,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:02:57.000Z","msg":"身體最鐘意高卡路里高熱量食物 例如脂肪 糖 <br />\n<br />\n你試下食完個麥當勞去抽血 會成支血都係脂肪 <br />\n<br />\n脂肪同糖係好快比身體吸收"},{"pid":"23eb50856a5a0c90ec4d5a79cae5c99a2dd55422","tid":766578,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T02:14:38.000Z